{"tid":2255097,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首兩季26警被捕 敏感崗位警員下周自願驗毒 高層升職要證身家清白","createTime":"2020-10-23T09:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T10:35:45.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"258fdfc7f2b47b7b44b6a88a31cffa5cb2974438","tid":2255097,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"今年首兩季有26名警務人員「知法犯法」被拘捕，今年5月更爆出西九龍總區反黑組人員涉嫌販毒。警方日前選擇性邀請部份傳媒受訪，稱早前成立的「誠信審核行動小組」將於下周正式推出驗毒計劃，首階段對象為「敏感崗位」人員，但<span class=\"red\">僅屬自願性質</span>。警方於7月起亦將要求參與高級警司、警司及總督察晉升選拔的人員提交「個人財政狀況聲明」，但<span class=\"red\">毋須接受審查</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年首兩季，因「知法犯法」被警隊拘捕的正規警務人員達26人。劉志聰稱，「誠信審核行動小組」至今已主動介入調查6宗案件，包括 「盜竊」、「與不良分子為伍」等案件。小組又透露，有跟進大埔警區特別職務隊一名警長涉嫌監守自盜，取走兩副麻雀自用，小組會就證物處理程序作專題研究，檢視執行上的困難等，又明言：「亦都係保障人員避免受到不必要指控。」"},{"pid":"4493f2bf2c1c945d7c2bb5e23c64efd7420cda8f","tid":2255097,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:33:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/XL4PBXJK2ZE4JAB2JQM2D4OXNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2FXL4PBXJK2ZE4JAB2JQM2D4OXNA%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vFHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=5d6f0ed1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2FXL4PBXJK2ZE4JAB2JQM2D4OXNA%2F&h=1965b9d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/XL4PBXJK2ZE4JAB2JQM2D4OXNA/</a>"},{"pid":"7a21150bacc7eda42657724c625024b3f8b3b629","tid":2255097,"uid":173016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"好想cap大和田個張  吓？吓？吓？"},{"pid":"482b7bfd504b0a4aab202e11c2af89015ffd156f","tid":2255097,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17970df8fdea5a87026963060c8947fb91c7aa2